Layer 2   Constraint Pressure Engine (CPI)        [ M-02 ]
----------------------------------------------------------------
Pressure score (unchanged):      P = σ(β·x)  
Directional classifier (light GBT, 15 features) returns dir ∈
    {capacity_creation, capacity_failure, ambiguous}

Output pressure_evt_v2
{
  entity_id  : string
  ts         : int64
  pressure   : float   // neutral magnitude
  direction  : enum {POSITIVE, NEGATIVE, AMBIGUOUS}
}

Layer 3   Causal Graph Fabric                     [ M-03 ]
----------------------------------------------------------------
Edge record  edge_v2
{
  src, dst        : string
  weight          : float   // signed strength (−1…+1)
  polarity        : enum {+1, −1}
  confidence      : float   // NEW, bootstrap  =  FDR-adj. p-value complement
  method          : string  // e.g. "PCMCI+TE"
  last_updated    : int64
}

Layer 4   Cascade Resonance Index (CRI 2.1)       [ M-04 ]
----------------------------------------------------------------
Before log() every component is mapped to its empirical CDF over a 30-day rolling window:
    x̃  =  percentile_rank(x)        // 0…1  
    log_term = log( x̃ + ε )

logCRI = Σ θ_k · log_term_k ,  k ∈ {A,C,I,V,D}

Layer 5   Propagation Baseline & Null-Cascade    [ M-05 ]
----------------------------------------------------------------
Add test harness that injects 500 synthetic “high-activity / low-causality” patterns per week.
Acceptance gate: system must suppress ≥95 % (FNR ≤5 %).

